{
  "title": "Controller Deep Dive",
  "uid": "controller-deep-dive",
  "tags": [
    "platform-mvp",
    "controller",
    "debug"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "10s",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Controller Logs",
      "type": "logs",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 16,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{namespace=\"default\"} |~ \"(?i)(regionalwidgetrequest|reconcil|spoke|created|error|widget)\"",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Kubernetes Events \u2014 Controller & Spoke",
      "type": "logs",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8,
        "w": 16,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{job=\"kubernetes-events\"} |~ \"(?i)(widget|kro|regional|binding)\"",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Reconcile Throughput (by result)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 14,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(controller_runtime_reconcile_total{controller=\"regionalwidgetrequest\"}[2m])",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{result}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Reconcile Latency Heatmap",
      "type": "heatmap",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 14,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(controller_runtime_reconcile_time_seconds_bucket{controller=\"regionalwidgetrequest\"}[2m])) by (le)",
          "refId": "A",
          "format": "heatmap"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Auth Flow & Connection Architecture",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 6
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "## Multi-Cluster Auth Flow\n\n```\nHub (kind-hub)                         Spoke (kind-us)\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500                      \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nKro RGD expands\n    \u2193\nRegionalWidgetRequest\n    \u2193 (watched by controller)\nController.Reconcile()\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u25001. Read spec.region = \"us\"\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u25002. Provider.Get(ctx, \"us\")\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500 ClusterProfile/us lookup\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500 Kubeconfig Secret read\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500 rest.Config built\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500 spokeClient created\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u25003. ensureWidget() \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2192 Widget created on spoke\n    \u2502\n    \u2514\u25004. Widget operator reconciles\n                                           \u2193\n                                    Widget.status updated on spoke\n\nAuth: Kubeconfig (X.509 client cert)\n      stored in Secret, referenced by ClusterProfile\n      No OIDC \u2014 service-to-service, not user-facing\n```",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Work Queue Depth",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 19,
        "w": 4,
        "h": 3
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "controller_runtime_active_workers{controller=\"regionalwidgetrequest\"}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 10
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Success Rate (2m)",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 19,
        "w": 4,
        "h": 3
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(controller_runtime_reconcile_total{controller=\"regionalwidgetrequest\",result=\"success\"}[2m])) / sum(rate(controller_runtime_reconcile_total{controller=\"regionalwidgetrequest\"}[2m]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.8
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.95
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "Spoke API Latency (rest_client)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 22,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(rest_client_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, rate(rest_client_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "p50"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39
}